00:39:52,302 --> 00:39:53,826
<i>Thank you.</i>

526
00:39:55,382 --> 00:39:58,384
<i>I'll treat you to pork belly if you
pass the intern interview.</i>

527
00:39:58,384 --> 00:40:01,523
<i>I'll treat you to pork belly
even if you fail.</i>

528
00:40:01,523 --> 00:40:04,112
<i>Keep it up today too!</i>

529
00:40:04,112 --> 00:40:05,913
<i>Mister Byun, stay strong!</i>

530
00:40:05,913 --> 00:40:09,472
<i>Byun Hyuk! We love you!</i>

531
00:40:57,155 --> 00:40:58,757
Hello.

532
00:41:31,759 --> 00:41:33,387
Thank you.

533
00:41:33,947 --> 00:41:38,757
Joon, you know the new guy
