is the best, Joon.

548
00:42:22,722 --> 00:42:24,637
It's the red chili paste that's good.

549
00:42:24,637 --> 00:42:29,501
Gangsu Foods does make really
great red chili paste, right?

550
00:42:29,501 --> 00:42:31,027
I suppose so.

551
00:42:39,940 --> 00:42:41,298
Joon.

552
00:42:42,123 --> 00:42:44,253
Try this red chili paste.

553
00:42:44,253 --> 00:42:45,809
Your dad developed this.

554
00:42:45,809 --> 00:42:47,681
- Really?
- Yes.

555
00:42:51,637 --> 00:42:53,478
Oh, it's spicy.

556
00:42:53,478 --> 00:42:55,159
So spicy!

557
00:42:56,648 --> 00:42:59,155
Joon, don't forget this taste.

558
00:42:59,155 --> 00:43:01,896
This will become the
base of Gangsu Foods.

559
00:43:01,896 --> 00:43:03,963
So spicy, so spicy.

560
00:43:12,356 --> 00:43:13,969
By the way...

561
00:43:13,969 --> 00:43:16,364
how are the preparations
for the intern test going

562
00:43:16,364 --> 00:43:17,675
