563
00:43:17,675 --> 00:43:19,547
Not bad.

564
00:43:20,108 --> 00:43:22,123
When is it?

565
00:43:23,442 --> 00:43:25,010
Tomorrow.

566
00:43:27,067 --> 00:43:29,574
- You can do it!
- We can!

567
00:43:33,615 --> 00:43:35,048
We're not late, are we?

568
00:43:35,048 --> 00:43:36,998
- We still have five minutes.
- Okay.

569
00:43:39,090 --> 00:43:42,150
<i>[Gangsu Food Intern Screening Test]</i>

570
00:43:46,971 --> 00:43:48,427
Mister Lee, Mister Kim, Madam Ahn!

571
00:43:48,427 --> 00:43:49,760
Good luck!

