All right, I'll treat.

729
00:57:16,945 --> 00:57:18,858
Wow. Yeah!

730
00:57:18,858 --> 00:57:21,438
Yeah!

731
00:57:22,561 --> 00:57:24,650
He's not a normal applicant.

732
00:57:24,650 --> 00:57:26,820
Splitting his money in half.

733
00:57:26,820 --> 00:57:29,496
That's ridiculous humanism.

734
00:57:29,496 --> 00:57:32,039
This doesn't suit Gangsu Foods.

735
00:57:32,039 --> 00:57:36,670
If we try to keep a monopoly,
we will fall into ruin one of these days.

736
00:57:36,670 --> 00:57:40,489
It's important to be
sensitive and ethical.

737
00:57:40,489 --> 00:57:43,139
I think it's a good mindset to have.

738
00:57:46,492 --> 00:57:50,893
Then since it is not unanimous...

739
00:57:50,893 --> 00:57:53,574
I will put him in the fail pile.

740
00:58:15,041 --> 00:58:17,989
So, have the decisions been made?

741
00:58:17,989 --> 00:58:20,762
What happened to Hyuk?

742
00:58:34,226 --> 00:58:37,231
<i>He failed in the unanimous vote.</i>

743
00:58:47,110 --> 00:58:50,847
So, I used my wild card.

744
00:58:50,847 --> 00:58:52,708
Wild card?

745
00:58:54,481 --> 00:58:56,539
Then that means...

746
00:58:57,483 --> 00:59:01,369
I don't think re-signing
your contract will work out.

747
00:59:01,369 --> 00:59:04,541
Did Byun Hyuk, that kid, pass?

748
00:59:04,541 --> 00:59:07,954
That's how it worked out.
See you next time.

749
00:59:07,954 --> 00:59:09,668
Wait.

750
00:59:43,893 --> 00:59:47,322
Here it is, Father. I passed.

751
00:59:48,699 --> 00:59:52,240
Please directly hire the cleaning staff
just as you promised.

752
00:59:52,240 --> 00:59:54,952
- Also...
- What now?

753
00:59:54,952 --> 00:59:58,219
Allow them to eat in the cafeteria.

754
01:00:11,364 --> 01:00:12,432
Shall we go?

755
01:00:52,976 --> 01:00:54,230
Hello.

756
01:00:54,230 --> 01:00:59,166
I'm the Strategic Team intern, Byun Hyuk.

757
01:00:59,166 --> 01:01:01,623
Let's work well together.

758
01:01:10,382 --> 01:01:11,818
Good morning.

759
01:01:11,818 --> 01:01:14,659
