the internship too though.

765
01:01:36,623 --> 01:01:37,641
Yeah.

766
01:01:42,530 --> 01:01:45,657
Hello. I'm Baek Joon.

767
01:01:46,402 --> 01:01:47,568
Please sit.

768
01:01:52,445 --> 01:01:54,505
Tell us your positive trait.

769
01:01:54,505 --> 01:01:58,335
Mine is that I have
many types of work experience.

770
01:01:58,335 --> 01:01:59,625
What kind of experience?

771
01:01:59,625 --> 01:02:04,384
I have paid my own tuition and
expenses since first year of college.

772
01:02:04,384 --> 01:02:07,233
I've had many part-time jobs.

773
01:02:07,233 --> 01:02:11,974
From tutoring students, being a
hotel maid, and a catering server...

774
01:02:11,974 --> 01:02:14,775
Tiling at construction sites,
designated driving

775
01:02:14,775 --> 01:02:17,576
doing sales at the mall,
and being a barista.

776
01:02:17,576 --> 01:02:20,472
I think I've had more experience
than most my age.

777
01:02:21,971 --> 01:02:25,132
Perhaps, you're not good at
sticking at one thing.

778
01:02:25,132 --> 01:02:30,311
I like to think I'm a multi-player
who can do many things at once.

779
01:02:31,271 --> 01:02:34,014
What's your motivation
for applying for Gangsu Foods?

780
01:02:35,199 --> 01:02:38,768
I had to prove that I wasn't a coward.

781
01:02:39,356 --> 01:02:42,230
Not to anyone else, but myself.

782
01:02:44,590 --> 01:02:46,307
You're a coward.

783
01:02:51,005 --> 01:02:53,235
I've done that now.

784
01:02:53,235 --> 01:02:55,443
Coming this far was enough.

785
01:02:55,443 --> 01:02:57,851
Do you have any last words
you want to say?

786
01:02:58,918 --> 01:03:01,007
Do not choose me.

787
01:03:04,184 --> 01:03:07,188
I will not be an intern here.

788
01:03:14,679 --> 01:03:16,516
Why are you being so stubborn?

789
01:03:16,516 --> 01:03:17,570
About what?

790
01:03:17,570 --> 01:03:20,539
You got notice that you passed,
so why didn't you go into work?

791
01:03:20,539 --> 01:03:22,903
Why did you go back there?

792
01:03:23,588 --> 01:03:26,126
I told you that I think
full-time work is silly.

793
01:03:26,126 --> 01:03:28,947
And working as
a contract cleaner is okay?

794
01:03:28,947 --> 01:03:32,447
I'm different than the others.
I'm only a part-time contract worker.

795
01:03:32,447 --> 01:03:34,849
It's just about freedom. That's all...

796
01:03:34,849 --> 01:03:37,998
I can leave whenever I want.

797
01:03:38,980 --> 01:03:42,762
How sincere are you?

798
01:03:43,298 --> 01:03:45,697
- What do you mean?
- With Hyuk.

799
01:03:45,697 --> 01:03:49,103
I'm asking if you're interested in him
as more than a friend.

800
01:03:50,820 --> 01:03:55,297
Why do I have to tell you that?

801
01:03:56,780 --> 01:03:58,572
Because it bothers me.

802
01:03:59,637 --> 01:04:01,039
Why?

803
01:04:01,574 --> 01:04:03,809
Why would it bother you?

804
01:04:10,797 --> 01:04:13,784
Did you forget?
I'm in charge of looking after Hyuk.

805
01:04:13,784 --> 01:04:16,592
I should know what the people
around Hyuk are thinking.

806
01:04:16,592 --> 01:04:21,135
So, you need to know
my feelings on Hyuk too?

807
01:04:21,135 --> 01:04:22,751
Is that it?

808
01:04:23,780 --> 01:04:25,806
Answer me.

809
01:04:25,806 --> 01:04:29,284
Do you... like Hyuk?

810
01:04:29,284 --> 01:04:31,914
<i>Yes, I do like it.</i>

811
01:04:31,914 --> 01:04:35,094
Mix coffee, drip coffee,
espresso. I like it all.

812
01:04:35,094 --> 01:04:37,914
Oh, really? Then go make some.

813
01:04:37,914 --> 01:04:39,885
- Me?
- Yes, you.

814
01:04:39,885 --> 01:04:42,474
The intern should go.
Should I do it, then?

815
01:04:42,474 --> 01:04:44,396
Yes, I will.

816
01:05:05,978 --> 01:05:08,824
Here you go. Recharge yourself.

817
01:05:10,951 --> 01:05:13,340
- Oh, Byun Hyuk.
- Yes?

818
01:05:13,340 --> 01:05:15,960
This is one of the companies
we work with.

819
01:05:15,960 --> 01:05:17,760
Get them to stamp this with their seal.

820
01:05:17,760 --> 01:05:18,900
I should do it?

821
01:05:18,900 --> 01:05:21,751
Yes, it's not hard at all.
Just get them to stamp it.

822
01:05:21,751 --> 01:05:25,260
Think of it as
your first job as the intern.

823
01:05:25,260 --> 01:05:26,550
You can do a good job, right?

824
01:05:26,550 --> 01:05:29,710
Of course. I can do a good job.

825
01:05:29,710 --> 01:05:31,108
Take a look here.

826
01:05:31,108 --> 01:05:35,018
Here, here, and here.

827
01:05:35,018 --> 01:05:37,215
Get them to stamp it
with their legal seal.

828
01:05:38,418 --> 01:05:41,092
- You know what that is, right?
- Yes.

829
01:05:43,827 --> 01:05:45,347
I'll succeed and return.

830
01:05:45,347 --> 01:05:48,913
So, the factory is
in Gyeonggi-do, Anseong?

831
01:05:48,913 --> 01:05:51,260
Get a car from the admin team.

832
01:05:51,260 --> 01:05:52,938
Yes, I will.

833
01:05:59,280 --> 01:06:01,778
This is your first task?

834
01:06:01,778 --> 01:06:04,280
Yes, I just need them
to stamp their seal.

835
01:06:04,280 --> 01:06:06,889
Still, they gave this to an intern?

836
01:06:06,889 --> 01:06:09,329
Yes, I just need to get it stamped.

837
01:06:09,329 --> 01:06:14,130
I just don't think this will be
easy to get resolved on your own.

838
01:06:14,130 --> 01:06:17,264
It's okay. I just
need to get it stamped.

839
01:06:18,528 --> 01:06:20,230
Why are you here anyway?

840
01:06:20,230 --> 01:06:22,990
Could you possibly be
my designated driver?

841
01:06:22,990 --> 01:06:24,190
A driver? Why?

842
01:06:24,190 --> 01:06:27,974
My license is suspended
until the end of the month.

843
01:06:27,974 --> 01:06:29,545
Could you help me?

844
01:06:32,320 --> 01:06:33,572
Answer me.

845
01:06:33,572 --> 01:06:36,862
Do you... like Hyuk?

846
01:06:39,161 --> 01:06:41,605
Okay. 50,000 won, deal?

847
01:06:41,605 --> 01:06:43,101
Deal.

848
01:07:02,369 --> 01:07:04,679
I think this is the right place.

849
01:07:05,692 --> 01:07:07,565
No one's here though.

850
01:07:12,335 --> 01:07:13,894
Joon.

851
01:07:13,894 --> 01:07:16,724
You shouldn't just go in there.

852
01:07:16,724 --> 01:07:18,360
Is anyone here?

853
01:07:18,360 --> 01:07:19,639
Joon...

854
01:07:19,639 --> 01:07:21,525
Excuse me!

855
01:07:28,889 --> 01:07:30,411
Anyone here?

856
01:07:31,217 --> 01:07:32,836
Is no one here?

857
01:07:32,836 --> 01:07:34,045
Joon.

858
01:07:38,143 --> 01:07:39,396
It's open.

859
01:07:44,358 --> 01:07:46,253
Hello.

860
01:07:49,422 --> 01:07:52,702
Is it okay to just go in? Is this okay?

861
01:07:52,702 --> 01:07:54,594
Is no one here?

862
01:08:07,552 --> 01:08:09,119
What's wrong, Joon?

863
01:08:23,280 --> 01:08:30,280
Subtitles by DramaFever

864
01:08:46,429 --> 01:08:50,006
<i>[Revolutionary Love]</i>

865
01:08:50,006 --> 01:08:51,501
<i>She's a strange girl.</i>

866
01:08:51,501 --> 01:08:54,635
<i>She's not someone who would be
hanging around with Byun Hyuk.</i>

867
01:08:54,635 --> 01:08:55,793
<i>Look into Baek Joon.</i>

868
01:08:55,793 --> 01:08:58,003
<i>Find out why she's always with Hyuk.</i>

869
01:08:58,003 --> 01:09:00,414
<i>What are you doing?
Are you looking into my background?</i>

870
01:09:00,414 --> 01:09:02,731
<i>Why am I here? Did you kidnap me?</i>

871
01:09:02,731 --> 01:09:04,717
<i>Negotiate with them and get it.</i>

872
01:09:04,717 --> 01:09:06,045
<i>How can I do that?</i>

873
01:09:06,045 --> 01:09:07,059
<i>How can they do this, Jae Hoon?</i>

874
01:09:07,059 --> 01:09:09,670
<i>Do I have to resolve work issues for you?
Figure it out yourself.</i>

875
01:09:09,670 --> 01:09:11,020
<i>Are you getting other ideas?</i>

876
01:09:11,020 --> 01:09:12,448
<i>Are you feeling bad
for your friend, Hyuk?</i>

877
01:09:12,448 --> 01:09:15,038
<i>I wish you would be
different than typical employees.</i>

878
01:09:15,038 --> 01:09:18,645
<i>If I do become different like you say,
can I be a man to you?</i>

